The '''Mos Eisley Police Station''', also known informally as '''city jail''',<ref name="Inside" /> was the main building and headquarters for the [[Mos Eisley Police Authority|Mos Eisley Police Department]] and it was where they kept their prisoners.<ref name="WEG">{{WEGCite|story=There's Many a Slip Betwixt Cup and Lip|book=Mos Eisley Adventure Set}}</ref> By [[0 ABY/Legends|0 ABY]], the jail was overcrowded.<ref name="Inside" />

[[File:Mos-eisley-police-station-plan.jpg|thumb|left|Floor plan of the Mos Eisley Police Station]]
Though it was a simple local law enforcement facility located in the city's main [[Mos Eisley/Legends|spaceport]], [[Stormtrooper/Legends|stormtroopers]] in [[0 BBY/Legends|0 BBY]] used its holding cells to detain the [[Tonnika sisters/Legends|Tonnika sisters]] (in reality [[Shada D'ukal]] and [[Karoly D'ulin]] in disguise) for [[Grand Moff/Legends|Grand Moff]] [[Argon (Grand Moff)|Argon]]. Also, at least one [[Mos Eisley cop|officer]] was planning on detaining [[BoShek/Legends|BoShek]] at the site on behalf of the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperials]]. [[Big Bunji/Legends|Big Bunji]] was once detained there.<ref name="WEG" />

Along with holding cells the building contained a storeroom for rations, a room for checking the weapons of suspects, and an area for interrogating prisoners.

